data.title: A Funny Thing Happened When I Was Typing My Suicide Note... - The Bigger Picture
data.description: I was going to kill myself two and a half weeks ago. Calm down, it's cool; I didn't. I'm sure most of you who follow me have seen me post about how long it's been since I quit alcohol.
